    "description": "<p class=\"pf0\"><span class=\"cf0\">When you deal Elemental or Mystical damage with an Attack, you gain Resistance (1) to that damage for 1 Round.</span></p><p class=\"pf0\"><span class=\"cf0\">If you deal Elemental or Mystical damage again while this is already active, you can choose to keep the current Resistance or switch it out for the new one instead.</span></p><p></p><p><em><strong>System Tip:</strong> Use this item to apply the effect.</em></p>",
